<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>Pidurangala Rock or Sigiriya Rock?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>But if there are two rocks, which one should I climb? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sigiriya-lion-rock\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sigiriya Lion Rock<\/a> has a lot of interesting history because it used to be King Kassapa&#x2019;s palace. Its beauty and history led it to be awarded <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/destinations\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\">UNESCO world heritage<\/a> status because of its incredible murals, gardens, and ruins. There&#x2019;s even a swimming pool on top of the rock! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114143\/best-viewpoint-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"best viewpoint sigiriya rock Pidurangala sri lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"best viewpoint sigiriya rock Pidurangala sri lanka\" class=\"wp-image-34179 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114143\/best-viewpoint-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114143\/best-viewpoint-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114143\/best-viewpoint-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114143\/best-viewpoint-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114143\/best-viewpoint-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.co