 beautiful it is. Additionally, the entrance fee is on the high side, priced at 30 USD.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--visa \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--visa\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"http:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/get-visa-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Order your visa for Sri Lanka easily online here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114118\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-top-2-590x810.jpg\" alt=\"sigiriya lion rock sri lanka-top\"><\/noscript><img width=\"246\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sigiriya lion rock sri lanka-top\" data-id=\"34198\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114118\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-top-2.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=34198\" class=\"wp-image-34198 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114118\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-top-2-590x810.jpg 590w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114118\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-top-2-300x412.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114118\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-top-2-600x824.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114118\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri