" target=\"_blank\">Sigiriya Lion Rock<\/a>.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Find all hotels in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sigiriya-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sigiriya<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/dambulla-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dambulla<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala.jpg\" alt=\"sunrise sigiriya rock Pidurangala\"><\/noscript><img width=\"278\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sunrise sigiriya rock Pidurangala\" class=\"wp-image-34186 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1578px) 100vw, 1578px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala.jpg 1578w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-300x365.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-600x730.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-493x600.jpg 493w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-666x810.jpg 666w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-278x338.jpg 278w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-1262x1536.jpg 1262w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-25x30.jpg 25w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-134x163.jpg 134w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-148x180.jpg 148w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-631x768.jpg 631w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-842x1024.jpg 842w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-888x1080.jpg 888w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-1184x1440.jpg 1184w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala-25x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114126\/sunrise-sigiriya-rock-Pidurangala.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Another bonus of choosing Pidurangala is that the entrance fee is only 500 LKR (3 USD)! Due to its pricing, it is also the most popular with backpackers and budget travelers. Both rocks are a must-visit but for adventure and view, Pidurangala is the absolute winner.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Like to visit both? <\/strong>Climb Pidu during sunrise and Sigiriya Lion Rock at sunset!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33584&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114058\/pidurangala-rock-sigiriyas-best-viewpoint-scaled.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114058\/pidurangala-rock-sigiriyas-best-viewpoint-16x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/