er noopener\">Dambulla<\/a>, which is a 30-minute tuk-tuk ride to Sigiriya.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-34205 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114106\/hike-Pidurangala-rock-sri-lanka-