> is located 30 minutes away but has more accommodations on offer in every price category. Most of the accommodation in Sigiriya is a bit higher in price but it does allow you to enjoy, and make the most, of the incredible scenery in this area. Some hotels even have direct views from the rooms of the rocks themselves!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Find all hotels in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sigiriya-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sigiriya<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/dambulla-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dambulla<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation.jpg\" alt=\"Sigiriya accommodation\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"331\" alt=\"Sigiriya accommodation\" class=\"wp-image-34202 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation-300x221.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation-600x442.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation-800x589.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content