nrises are clear.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>Don&#x2019;t forget to bring water into your reusable water bottle because there is no option to buy it. You&#x2019;ll need it for the climb! <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here&#x2019;s how to reduce plastic while traveling<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"On top of Pidurangala Rock Experience the sunrise from the top of Pidurangala Rock where the first rays of light hit the surrounding landscape and the morning mist clears from the surrounding jungles. It&#x2019;s a magical spot and moment that&#x2019;s not to be missed in Sri Lanka. The large boulder, the highest point, has more [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":34186,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_relevanssi_hide_post":"","_relevanssi_pin_for_all":"","_relevanssi_pin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_unpin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_include_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_exclude_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_no_append":"","_relevanssi_related_not_related":"","_relevanssi_related_posts":"19406,1289,10626,20659,8685,19879"},"categories":[5245,75,9],"tags":[38,6625,54],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v19.3 (Yoast SEO v19.7.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plug